    "# Mentorship Matching Demo\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook is a GitHub-safe, anonymized version of the mentorship matching workflow. It contains no real student or alumni data. Use the sample CSVs for demonstration, or upload your own CSVs in Google Colab.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Privacy note:** never commit real survey exports, student data, alumni data, emails, IDs, or match outputs to GitHub."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "1da88d83",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Setup\n",
    "\n",
    "Run this cell first. It makes the local `src/` package available whether the notebook is opened from the repository root or from the `notebooks/` folder."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "57f3326f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "import sys\n",
    "\n",
    "# Resolve project root for both local Jupyter and Google Colab-style execution.\n",
    "current_dir = Path.cwd()\n",
    "project_root = current_dir if (current_dir / \"src\").exists() else current_dir.parent\n",
    "if str(project_root) not in sys.path:\n",
    "    sys.path.insert(0, str(project_root))\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Project root: {project_root}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "81830940",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Import matching modules"
